org.gradoop.common.model.impl.id

Class GradoopIdSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<GradoopId>
        • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.id.GradoopIdSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<GradoopId>, Collection<GradoopId>, Set<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.core.io.IOReadableWritable, org.apache.flink.types.Value

    public class GradoopIdSet
extends AbstractSet<GradoopId>
implements org.apache.flink.types.Value
    Represents a set of GradoopId instances, ignoring any duplicates. Note that by implementing List Flink uses the Kryo serializer for (de-)serializing the list.
    See Also:
    GradoopId, Serialized Form
